articles.author: Brian Gallagher
articles.title: Stephen Amell does NOT support the 'myopic' SAG-AFTRA strike - Daily Mail
articles.description: While it's clear that the SAG-AFTRA strike is supported by a vast majority of the guild - with 97.91% of SAG authorizing the strike in June - some don't support, like Stephen Amell.
